OL,3,CWheelchair-user says Blue Badge fraud
OL,4,C'ruins lives'
OL,6,FA wheelchair user from Aylesbury says
OL,7,Fdrivers who misuse disabled parking
OL,8,Fbays 'ruin lives'.
OL,10,FSimon Pinnell says he needs the wider
OL,11,Fdisabled bays to get in and out of his
OL,12,Fvehicle but he often can't find a
OL,13,Fspace because they're being used by
OL,14,Fable-bodied people.
