OL,3,CWheelchair-user says Blue Badge fraud
OL,4,C'ruins lives'
OL,6,F'It doesn't kill people but it ruins
OL,7,Fpeople's lives', Simon Pinnell told
OL,8,FITV News Meridian
OL,10,FBuckinghamshire Council seized 11 Blue
OL,11,FBadges during a recent 10-day
OL,12,Foperation to crack down on their
OL,13,Fmisuse.
OL,15,FAs a result, some of the owners are
OL,16,Fnow facing potential prosecution.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
