OL,3,CWheelchair-user says Blue Badge fraud
OL,4,C'ruins lives'
OL,6,FSteven Broadbent, the Cabinet Member
OL,7,Ffor Transport at Buckinghamshire
OL,8,FCouncil said: "Last year alone in
OL,9,FBuckinghamshire we also fined, through
OL,10,Fpenalty charge notice, almost 2,500
OL,11,Fpeople for parking in a disabled bay
OL,12,Fwhen they don't have a Blue Badge at
OL,13,Fall.
OL,15,F"So this is about making sure that
OL,16,FBlue Badge holders are genuine and
OL,17,Fbeing used in the correct way but also
OL,18,Fabout making sure that people aren't
OL,19,Fmisusing disabled bays."
