OL,3,CWheelchair-user says Blue Badge fraud
OL,4,C'ruins lives'
OL,6,F"It's very frustrating. I'm not a
OL,7,Fperson to normally complain, I'm very
OL,8,Fgrateful for my situation and the fact
OL,9,FI'm still able to go out and live my
OL,10,Flife but it adds a level of
OL,11,Fcomplication that I don't need and
OL,12,Fit's really frustrating and sometimes
OL,13,Fit can ruin my day.
OL,15,FIsabelle says it can 'ruin her day'
OL,17,F"I've seen this person park in the
OL,18,Fexact same disabled space since
OL,19,FSeptember with no Blue Badge and it's
OL,20,Fa 70 pound fine every time and I guess
OL,21,Fit's pocket change to them.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
