OL,3,CWheelchair-user says Blue Badge fraud
OL,4,C'ruins lives'
OL,6,F"Aside from the fines, there's been no
OL,7,Factual repercussions. If finances
OL,8,Faren't enough of a repercussion for
OL,9,Fsomebody then something else should
OL,10,Fhappen."
OL,12,FSimon agrees there should be much
OL,13,Ftougher penalties: "Ideally what I'd
OL,14,Flike to happen is for the abuse of
OL,15,FBlue Badge spaces to be seen in the
OL,16,Fsame light as drink driving.
OL,18,F"It doesn't kill people but it ruins
OL,19,Fpeople's lives."
